sources.title: Voyage to the Prehistoric Planet 1965 | Roger Corman, Basil Rathbone | Adventure, Sci-Fi
sources.description:
In 2020, after the colonization of the moon, 3 spaceships Vega, Sirius and Capella set out to explore the planet Venus. Upon reaching their destination, they discover a planet teeming with dinosaurs and a dubious trace of an advanced and hidden civilization.

Directors: Curtis Harrington, Pavel Klushantsev
Writer: Curtis Harrington
Stars: Basil Rathbone, Faith Domergue, Marc Shannon 
Genres: Classics, Cult Film, Roger Corman, Adventure, Sci-Fi
